    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-11-02T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-11-02T00:00:00-05:00" n="91"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d91">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">
                    <persName corresp="#p_RFD1">Roosevelt</persName> Papers: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">President</gloss> to the Ambassador in
                        the United Kingdom</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_WJG1" type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Winant</hi>
                    </persName>)<note n="1" xml:id="d91fn1">Sent to the United States Naval Attach,
                        London, via the White House Map Room and Navy channels.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                        <lb/>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">priority</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Hyde Park</hi>
                        </placeName>?] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-11-02">2 November
                            1943</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Personal and secret from the President to <persName corresp="#p_WJG1"
                        >Winant</persName>.</p>
                <p>You are absolutely right. I will let you know as soon as date can be arranged and
                    you would meet us in North Africa.</p>
                <p>It will be good to see you again.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_RFD1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Roosevelt</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
